    "A participant from G A R described this feature as \"useful to quickly identify areas, and it helps you learn and observe things you can improve quite intuitively.\"",
    "Ease of use was also a significant point of appreciation.",
    "Participants described the system as \"really intuitive, user-friendly\" and \"clear, easy to use and methodical.\"",
    "Additionally, participants praised the quality of the suggestions offered.",
    "Comments like \"I liked that it gave useful suggestions that are actually valuable to a beginner\" and \"It gives me tips and advice on how I can improve the wording and formatting of my recipe, so I can easily make these changes to improve the clarity and how clear my recipe is\" were common."
